What you need to know:

The Uriri Constituency Development Fund-sponsored tournament organised by area MP Mark Nyamita attracted more than 50 teams in both men and women categoriesSpeaking during the awards ceremony, Nyamita and Migori Senator Ochilo Ayako lauded the participants for engaging in sportsAll the four wards in the Sub County were represented in the week-long tournament aimed at nurturing talents and empowering youths during the prolonged holidays occasioned by Covid-19